Clean-room derivation; no upstream code lifted verbatim. The skill
structure (SEV classification + PIR scaffold) was learned from the
inspiration, but every line in this directory was written
independently against Soleur's own PIR shape
(`knowledge-base/engineering/ops/post-mortems/dashboard-error-postmortem.md`),
GDPR Art. 33/34 obligations, and the `brand_survival_threshold`
3-tier vocabulary canonical to this repo.

